data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies.  BACK on the Market! $5k in buydown/closing costs! Single level home! Large lot! Don't miss the chance to see this 3-bedroom 2-bath home with a true two car garage. This home has been well taken care of and doesn't have tons of layers or DIY projects gone wrong. Great living room and kitchen layout with nice separation of three bedrooms down the hall. The backyard is inviting with a covered pergola and plenty of room to enjoy, & large sheds 8x12 & 8x24. Side area on the home fits an RV!
